{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "cbed35ae-b714-4cac-9a62-3dc607391d4e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 890.3662298828126,
      "y": 350.6250018554688,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM与事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f125fa79-3e95-4be6-ab65-c9d2426a9821",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": -4515.925924070458,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b8ed3364-48f0-4006-9d49-f0ca53f47e00",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -6164.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5ec58487-b4c5-4da2-93de-c6890c5cd6db",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6244.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM是文档对象模型，全称为Document Object Model",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c2a68d47-6d6f-4954-9a48-8eb77e909bae",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -6084.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM用一个逻辑树来表示一个文档，树的每个分支终点都是一个节点，每个节点都包含着对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a97115a0-367e-4974-bcc9-8abbfeee009e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -5471.4814796260125,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM选择器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ce31dca3-43cb-4ddb-b69a-00ed1ce38b6b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5924.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过id定位",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "02c150fe-7f62-4195-88cf-f4efb7f0b12c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5924.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "getElementById()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4b17f502-8062-47ed-abd7-b32b40702f19",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5924.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回匹配到id的第一个元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "45ca57f7-aadd-43bd-97da-0a7878b25f58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5764.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过class定位",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c2b300bc-2e88-42c8-952e-847b26a92dbd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5764.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "getElementsByClassName()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2aa1a1a-8ed5-44cd-b6d8-5880322732a0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5764.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回由匹配到的元素构成的HTMLCollection对象，它是一个类数组结构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "50403472-3d6a-4bda-aa99-f923af6d58da",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5604.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过name属性定位",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d12a4cdb-1bed-4f25-afe9-b2c910e0ef7a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5604.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "getElementsByName()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "998976a0-5051-484d-9126-a00605ec14a7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5604.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回由匹配到的元素构成的NodeList对象，它是一个类数组结构",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c944836f-8256-43fb-aab6-2451aee5e1f8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5444.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过标签名定位",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b6c99b40-b552-49a9-82fc-6e52846af75d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5444.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "getElementsByTagName()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "96959feb-7893-4fb7-a7d2-096c2df72871",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5444.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回由匹配到的元素构成的HTMLCollection对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "45134cc5-a53d-457f-8a77-563b5be9bf4b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -5204.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "querySelector选择器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "74bca3e9-9834-4b04-af5c-e342a26d274a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5284.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在基准元素下，选择器匹配到的元素集合中的第一个元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "03c2a672-0925-420a-b452-18e17244a9c6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5284.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回值为匹配到的第一个子元素。匹配的过程中不仅仅针对基准元素的后代元素，实际上会遍历整个文档结构，包括基准元素和它的后代元素以外的元素。实际处理过程是首先创建一个匹配元素的初始列表，然后判断每个元素是否为基准元素的后代元素，第一个属于基准元素的后代元素将会被返回",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b57b8989-ec62-4d6e-abcf-83076ab600f5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -5124.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "element = baseElement.querySelector(selectors)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "58376859-dab7-47ee-a521-e8d422865be9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -5124.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "selectors是一个标准的CSS选择器，而且必须是合法的选择器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4ab7f255-633c-4e4c-8c5f-36ecfbc4a5ad",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4884.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "querySelectorAll选择器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c64a1e5-3f34-4ff9-b1e5-ccc3c0792100",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4964.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "querySelectorAll选择器会返回基准元素下匹配到的所有子元素的集合",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c856b75a-7a1d-4e8c-90ad-21d2314f8aaa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -4964.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "querySelectorAll选择器匹配过程与querySelector选择器一样，优先获取所有匹配元素的集合，然后判断每个元素是否属于基准元素。如果属于则返回结果，最终返回一个NodeList对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c2db3812-1a76-4a31-8b3c-191c55f419eb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4804.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "elementList = baseElement.querySelectorAll(selectors);",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6e862f3b-80a8-44fc-a62a-439bb528350f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -4164.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "HTMLCollection对象与NodeList对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "830d301c-9ee1-4dc7-aeaa-ba9d874b7842",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4564.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获取方式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e8091092-a0db-40c0-8a91-cf155c307785",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4644.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素的children属性，返回的是HTMLCollection对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3e12a86b-12fd-46dd-ba68-7ea58bf84533",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4484.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素的childNodes属性，返回的是NodeList对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9854b414-95a9-43d8-8f22-4d5cd7e034fa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -4164.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "相同点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c00f0c8b-73f7-49c9-89a5-ce164687886a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4324.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "都是类数组对象，有length属性，可以通过call()函数或apply()函数处理成真正的数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5dedf4f8-7b79-47a1-9a1f-d68a0aeb7266",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4164.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "都有item()函数，通过索引定位元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1dfd4963-1941-4474-8a01-42bb5a8a3e96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -4164.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "item()函数通过序号来获取特定的某个节点，超过索引则返回“null”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3f89ae0c-3d61-4045-8a3a-ae6227bd837c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -4004.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "都是实时性的，DOM树的变化会及时反映到HTMLCollection对象和NodeList对象上，只是在某些函数调用的返回结果上会存在差异",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "41d5d6db-14e2-4d4b-88cb-bd383c3a4a68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -4004.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "querySelectorAll()获取的NodeList对象没有实时性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "166a1c91-2036-4c0f-8bc1-7a06d7b4dbdd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -3764.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不同点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "618bc5be-0da7-46a1-8f93-7257cdc8c754",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3844.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "HTMLCollection对象比NodeList对象多个namedItem()函数，可以通过id或者name属性定位元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a6ef8c4f-8651-4be8-94ab-50ba3c0e1f8b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -3844.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "namedItem()函数用来返回一个节点。首先通过id属性去匹配，然后如果没有匹配到则使用name属性匹配，如果还没有匹配到则返回“null”。当出现重复的id或者name属性时，只返回匹配到的第一个值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3c468854-c3e8-4cd4-bbba-ed6b6cbe2dd1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3684.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "HTMLCollection对象只包含元素的集合（Element），即具有标签名的元素；而NodeList对象是节点的集合，既包括元素，也包括节点，例如text文本节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c5d2b7a6-4336-485b-b2ec-25ace5d7ac6d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -2262.5925907371225,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见的DOM操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0a0e346b-2e4a-4bb2-a5c8-5a1c798292f3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -3044.814812959345,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "新增节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cf52233c-945a-4eea-9c0e-b04d25328d11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3524.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "新增元素节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ea71d0a2-cfb7-4f0c-bcba-b3db2e9c1f80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -3524.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "document.createElement(元素名)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "be549d22-d1bd-45ba-afe4-96f1e334f07d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3364.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "新创建一个属性节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6d442e7c-57e2-4b33-8946-13fdfcd5b0e0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -3364.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "document.createAttribute(属性名)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c2459b2-5140-4f84-b069-4f689f6dd2fd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3204.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将属性节点绑定在元素节点上",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5612607-214c-4e15-a736-187f7bd294dc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -3204.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.setAttributeNode(属性节点)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd151396-a623-476f-b806-997caa6b3949",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -3044.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点新增属性节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1b6fbd9f-64ac-4a44-9e4e-1f9673512949",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -3044.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.setAttribute(属性名, 属性值)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "07bf3554-a6d0-45f4-8f32-f8a0f55c874e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2884.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "新创建一个文本节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6bf534-d5c5-46fc-8487-3d8c3bc167de",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2884.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "document.createTextNode(文本内容)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3e70c86f-c1ec-48e0-a4b0-117e092e616d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2724.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将文本节点作为元素节点的子元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5979824-89f7-4d19-9462-b51cf43f967c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2724.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.appendChild(文本节点)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8657a506-8c50-451d-b323-b81c844bab11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2564.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将目标节点添加至第一个节点的前面",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9353ed0-8fca-48ba-8582-b56e64241329",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2564.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.insertBefore(目标节点, 第一个节点)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "47af73ea-9ee0-426e-af44-f3f1dcfc762e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -2218.14814629268,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "删除节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c345f2b8-f470-49c8-bc7f-8a3e9186cb4a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2404.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "删除元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c7b66be6-dc4c-4931-8833-8717ccb8e6b0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2404.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "父元素节点.removeChildren(待删除元素节点)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "63ba62e6-b770-4fc9-b7ee-8d4ac5433f53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": -2404.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "只支持删除元素节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "781cc033-56f7-45f8-af25-89c23c3c5b96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2244.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "删除属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e4150802-7f4c-4597-a39b-096688276242",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2244.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.removeAttribute(属性名)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cbb2ed36-7bf9-4ac9-8b2e-ab4bdf6ed950",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -2004.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "删除文本节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9f890381-a97c-4a96-a53a-7e19b5e5134c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -2084.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "父元素节点.removeChild(文本节点)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7fd99263-ac2b-4b1f-a698-1a13720d0770",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": -2084.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "支持删除非元素节点，比如文本节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "87e568dd-f0e1-47dc-b994-0bfd58970530",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -1924.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "父元素节点.innerHTML = ''",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d4806830-bf1c-439c-ad9f-725075eb1e73",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -1524.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f8397b8f-7a78-4baf-a97a-e80984e07390",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1764.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改元素节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a1f4e7c-2182-47d3-8988-aa0dbd46df4f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -1764.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "父元素节点.replaceChild(新元素节点，旧元素节点)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e24173bd-51f6-4fcc-969f-87171d7944f4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1524.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改属性节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "643197ec-28e3-4b38-9306-f4c6c00c764c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -1604.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.setAttribute(属性名, 属性值)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "83684d2c-5f77-4dd6-87fa-c598179d4677",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -1444.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.className = 属性值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ecc57643-7866-48de-8f8d-e693613cfb1f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1284.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改文本节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ad8abe17-7e0d-4b9f-a65c-5e79394c8783",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -1284.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素节点.interHTML = 修改值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bd88a2f2-a619-447b-bdb1-2223efc1ecb3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1310.3662298828126,
      "y": 5217.175927781394,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d6ab56a7-e400-4c91-b465-13a575810413",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": -644.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件流",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "449f630f-3c98-4c0f-a371-3f390fc2b340",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -1044.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e2047e6d-0483-4866-a23c-78b99da7d663",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -1124.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件流描述的是从页面中接收事件的顺序。事件发生后会在目标节点和根节点之间按照特定的顺序传播，路径经过的节点都会接收到事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "54fce86f-39a2-42c1-8191-16cdd3044e56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -964.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "一个完整的事件流实际包含了3个阶段：事件捕获阶段>事件目标阶段>事件冒泡阶段",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "09f3100f-765c-48bf-9da4-a7cc30df5062",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -644.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "完整事件流",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4ad640a1-3b0b-4797-9d89-1d528de16af0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -804.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件捕获",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23d60140-71c1-4c3e-89f9-5702e61d1a84",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -804.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件捕获阶段的主要表现是不具体的节点先接收事件，然后逐级向下传播，最具体的节点最后接收到事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7f3646b9-747a-45fe-aebb-cf9b25659d75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -644.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件目标",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6fe3a69-601f-4896-a7cf-88c9fafe9d69",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -644.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件目标阶段表示事件刚好传播到用户产生行为的元素上，可能是事件捕获的最后一个阶段，也可能是事件冒泡的第一个阶段",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e61235bd-6b18-4043-b168-a08d7c7b95b5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -484.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件冒泡",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "165294c2-3d38-4c68-b9f9-08463489be40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": -484.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件冒泡阶段的主要表现是最具体的元素先接收事件，然后逐级向上传播，不具体的节点最后接收事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4430d82e-d8cf-44eb-9e6d-88ff5d9b1a35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": -244.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "addEventListener",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "14488b5b-d85b-4371-b757-6d52314e461e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -324.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第三个参数默认为false时，按照冒泡型事件流处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b3f80406-f995-4ae3-92e6-353f9febc61b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": -164.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第三个参数默认为true时，按照捕获型事件流处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "590c801c-3608-4625-a7e9-96e86d885e9f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 1961.8518537073207,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "33c832e5-f451-4050-ae76-ad399fc2ae24",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 585.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4dc2a47d-289b-4cd9-8717-bf9c4be82de5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "56666826-cf0f-449a-8a46-c3802516aae7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 75.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将一个函数赋值给一个事件处理属性，有两种表现形式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "123c7561-631a-4eb3-be4b-c4f9bdebd76c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": -4.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第一种是先通过JavaScript代码获取DOM元素，再将函数赋值给对应的事件属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9699352c-b648-4c07-9bc0-f46d89b6f692",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": -4.814812959346,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var btn = document.getElementById(\"btn\"); \nbtn.onclick = function(){}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1c276cda-e1af-4aeb-8b9a-d57fa9582430",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 155.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第二种是直接在html中设置对应事件属性的值，值有两种表现形式，一种是执行的函数体，另一种是函数名，然后在script标签中定义该函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2ca35346-40f3-488d-93fc-cd077589592f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": 155.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "`<button onclick=\"alert('面试厅');\">`单击`</button>`\n`<button onclick=\"clickFn()\">`单击`</button>`\n\n`<script>`\n\n    function clickFn() {\n\n        alert('面试厅');\n\n    }\n\n`</script>`",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8094afb8-e297-435a-8e92-ed8b6aaf11f2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 315.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "以上两种DOM0级事件处理程序同时存在时，第一种在JavaScript中定义的事件处理程序会覆盖掉后面在html标签中定义的事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6da68f4d-bce7-49ba-8897-b24773cf263a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 475.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "需要注意的是，DOM0级事件处理程序只支持事件冒泡阶段",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c475a8ce-4d2b-48fe-88c7-d0986b581156",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 715.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "优缺点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "65be85e5-27da-431e-b38b-9eeb02903eb7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "优点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6489f734-cda4-459c-a44e-ca88380781ce",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "简单且可以跨浏览器",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1cc0f727-a6e4-4f90-acff-17ec9b11704e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "缺点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "abb2737d-61f8-44d3-9460-5ab76f6e405a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "一个事件处理程序只能绑定一个函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f13f0663-867d-47ad-a877-36fe92acf193",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "删除元素绑定的事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9dd3452-eb7f-491b-a06e-f809882c3851",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "只需要将对应的事件处理程序设置为null即可",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8f135cf7-2eea-46e3-97cc-9660910cd457",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "btn.onclick = null;",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1a6066b6-c553-4476-a252-605facacc858",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 1745.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM2",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "46f27f9e-3410-42bf-8de3-540cec5f3499",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "411b34c9-425d-4af4-98bf-87cc4a41e0e9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在DOM2级事件处理程序中，当事件发生在节点时，目标元素的事件处理函数就会被触发，而且目标元素的每个祖先节点也会按照事件流顺序触发对应的事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d67974ce-5bea-45c2-b72d-82279c1415e9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "针对DOM2级事件处理程序，不同的浏览器厂商制定了不同的实现方式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "db76e99e-8706-4ebc-adf6-5a05dcfec160",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在IE10及以下版本中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "85dd9e66-b592-4ed0-b126-d5c4583a94bb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 1275.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "只支持事件冒泡阶段",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "01566886-66aa-4205-aa53-1d7ee08d37a1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 1435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过attachEvent()函数添加事件处理程序，通过detachEvent()函数删除事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4d563215-e97a-428a-81d2-1dc57f9698c9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在IE11及其他非IE浏览器中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1d7828a6-b841-4cd8-8ba5-47cd1cf80621",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 1595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "同时支持事件捕获阶段与事件冒泡阶段",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a440a759-7118-43df-bc61-c483aa5e8395",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 1755.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过addEventListener()函数添加事件处理程序，通过removeEventListener()函数删除事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "533c9bf8-98bc-433d-a2f6-cb9d9f001633",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 1995.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "共同点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fa14f35d-8f5c-4fc2-9a12-5017eeb87b61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 1915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不管是IE浏览器还是非IE浏览器都支持对同一个事件绑定多个处理函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3b2bd06f-4b11-44d5-a512-66356343fa1d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2075.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在需要删除绑定的事件时，不能删除匿名函数，因为添加和删除的必须是同一个函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c9578144-f28e-4b1d-b8a1-92e0a43032e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 2355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不同点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e40cfa49-d479-42bb-a35b-75f379c22189",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "执行顺序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4e9e103c-edb9-41fa-b74f-1b47897ea8cf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在IE浏览器中，使用attachEvent()函数为同一个事件添加多个事件处理函数时，会按照添加的相反顺序执行。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a82262d-5e2d-4e85-a19a-669f6d3512e2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2475.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用域",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "98ccd43d-787f-4e2e-ba1d-4191d429d2a0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2395.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在IE浏览器下，使用attachEvent()函数添加的事件处理程序会在全局作用域中运行，因此this指向全局作用域window",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2edef9f-49f6-48fc-9eb6-b56debe7712a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在非IE浏览器下，使用addEventListener()函数添加的事件处理程序在指定的元素内部执行，因此this指向绑定的元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2b711c3-f2e0-451a-a495-27dcd0ac6a12",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 3555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM3",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "79ce6c69-c807-4e69-928b-116550471ac6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 3015.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3cb2e86d-9a9f-42ab-9a40-49dda708573e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 2715.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM3级事件处理程序是在DOM2级事件的基础上重新定义了事件，也添加了一些新的事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b00495a7-3dc5-4d21-a633-152ca4676b0c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 2715.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "​",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d6d8e1a7-50d4-4309-8e1e-d23dea4bfdf4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3315.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "最重要的区别在于DOM3级事件处理程序允许自定义事件，自定义事件由createEvent(\"CustomEvent\")函数创建，返回的对象有一个initCustomEvent()函数，通过传递对应的参数可以自定义事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8c9cdb07-fe91-4214-9652-aa98ce40fa7b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数可以接收以下4个参数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b4ceadad-8a3a-41ed-af06-271761a1a9c4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": 2875.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "type",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "461a2391-e753-49df-8c32-cb916a3e8bb4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4250.366229882813,
      "y": 2875.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "字符串、触发的事件类型、自定义，例如“keyDown”“selectedChange",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "15ae1c74-c2e5-4c13-9a79-b920ab01d21e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": 3035.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "bubble（布尔值）",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e2cfe0f5-dce7-4e35-9b1f-0c9d94076cd3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4250.366229882813,
      "y": 3035.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示事件是否可以冒泡",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "54c14f60-3a9a-4a4a-8f84-52701fd0005d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": 3195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "cancelable(布尔值）",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c01b9fb1-2a95-4ca4-a438-edef5ac16a3f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4250.366229882813,
      "y": 3195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示事件是否可以取消",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c256cc3c-99bb-4b0a-b97e-c1be7d8caa64",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": 3355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "detail（对象）",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5021c823-458b-4559-b95a-8518ed9b86e6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4250.366229882813,
      "y": 3355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "任意值，保存在event对象的detail属性中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9266bf4d-c4e5-4648-b429-17b8de7cc2e7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "创建完成的自定义事件，可以通过dispatchEvent()函数去手动触发，触发自定义事件的元素需要和绑定自定义事件的元素为同一个元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a57730ff-113e-47d4-8834-dff30e1ff49b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4095.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "实现",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e582b66-c6bc-4a46-a4d9-b8692353dcfd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "HTML",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "10126cbd-83ba-4bb4-aa35-517939b5fc92",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "`<div id=\"watchDiv\">`监听自定义事件的div元素`</div>`\n`<button id=\"btn\">`单击触发自定义事件`</button>`",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "89129e8e-41eb-4c8c-a79b-6169704f8668",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 3915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "创建自定义事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a8568b5d-35fb-4a01-95dc-be138e7db5f7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在创建自定义事件之前，需要判断浏览器是否支持DOM3级事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c235553c-eac3-4198-88c6-6c000a911fba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3830.3662298828126,
      "y": 3835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "document.implementation.hasFeature('CustomEvents', '3.0');",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f005b2cf-5a1d-4105-9dd2-3d76aa68e475",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 3995.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var customEvent;\n// 创建自定义事件\n\n(function () {\n\n    if (document.implementation.hasFeature('CustomEvents', '3.0')) {\n\n        var detailData = {name: 'kingx'};\n\n        customEvent = document.createEvent('CustomEvent');\n\n        customEvent.initCustomEvent('myEvent', true, false, detailData);\n\n    }\n\n})();",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "154beaca-760a-42e3-80ab-ae0de6163bf8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 4235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "监听自定义事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dc3dbf54-c446-4b64-9e74-2788cc2199e0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 4155.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过addEventListener()函数监听自定义的myEvent事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fca619b9-fe5f-4f28-b462-64eea21ec4b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 4315.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 获取元素\nvar div = document.querySelector('#watchDiv');\n\n// 监听myEvent事件\n\ndiv.addEventListener('myEvent', function (e) {\n\n    console.log('div监听到自定义事件的执行, 携带的参数为: ', e.detail);\n\n});",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4b1d76e3-44f8-41df-95bb-7870d2f4d19f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 4555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "触发自定义事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "20a07af5-d320-4f2c-9ca1-4e49f56295ba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 4475.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "通过dispatchEvent()函数触发myEvent事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a1de01a1-a3eb-48d2-97a2-39cea48f20c3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 4635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 获取元素\nvar btn = document.querySelector('#btn');\n\n// 绑定click事件，触发自定义事件\n\nbtn.addEventListener('click', function () {\n\n    div.dispatchEvent(customEvent);\n\n});",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "444ad961-9db9-4658-91d2-c9499811645d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 5515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Event对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a0e5f648-e006-4fea-b7c5-809916b09f58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 4795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "92255625-033f-48ea-9fa1-1a7d9fb7f154",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件在浏览器中是以Event对象的形式存在的，每触发一个事件，就会产生一个Event对象。该对象包含所有与事件相关的信息，包括事件的元素、事件的类型及其他与特定事件相关的信息",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "89848cc1-c7b9-4617-a3b0-e77fdbe0f0b9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 5035.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获取Event对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9e6a5f8b-2f63-4d30-a39e-d258a7965dad",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 4955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在事件处理程序中，Event对象会作为参数传入，参数名为event",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "71d14901-a94e-40fd-ad85-b5e818fb21d5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 4955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "推荐",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "15d6b368-86be-4cdd-a859-edb5105e030f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在事件处理程序中，通过window.event属性获取Event对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23547562-0801-4fd2-8563-f6350cbf3505",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不同浏览器有兼容性问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6702dc69-5a3a-4bcd-9cce-b4f074ac2c32",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 5355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获取事件的目标元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9ed9fafb-c2c9-4ca0-bca4-f5929b122d11",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5275.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在IE浏览器中，event对象使用srcElement属性来表示事件的目标元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "402e665f-db40-49e4-960b-202b2f27f394",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "而在非IE浏览器中，event对象使用target属性来表示事件的目标元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6678da85-d37c-4fde-adb6-d399ca85cbb5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 5675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "target属性与currentTarget属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "06a843fd-19e6-44a4-a886-df16c3a26b64",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "target属性在事件目标阶段，理解为真实操作的目标元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "05a97436-f72e-4536-9818-0bf917c4418e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在事件流的任何阶段，target属性始终指向的是实际操作的元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8a32e1cc-df9d-4228-8131-47d9d23c0c95",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5755.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "currentTarget属性在事件捕获、事件目标、事件冒泡这3个阶段，理解为当前事件流所处的某个阶段对应的目标元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b8698823-1a61-4dc1-86a3-80de25a5bc09",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 5995.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "阻止事件冒泡",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9d90e98e-3dc3-4255-8629-669ad853c778",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 5915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "stopPropagation",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3d3a699a-56cf-4c1f-b814-4953a6b73f36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 5915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "仅会阻止事件冒泡，其他事件处理程序仍然可以调用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7e33a9d0-7a76-431c-96fa-1657619d6867",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 5915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "推荐",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0a2a7dd9-f5d3-4307-b534-bd69e3c8afe1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6075.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "stopImmediatePropagation",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e09163ac-8030-4ac1-affe-54e7854a7287",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6075.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不仅会阻止冒泡，也会阻止其他事件处理程序的调用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7cf08f57-d4ed-495a-93b7-8167fbd048cb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 6075.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "阻止后续的事件执行",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3d6ea976-2623-41ab-94c6-c3e2b78ab70c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 6235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "阻止默认行为",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "257b7b8e-f09f-4c3f-9fd1-8ebbd866d559",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "event.preventDefault",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1b5e72bf-9b57-4bb8-9085-f5a767b043ff",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 6581.8518537073205,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件委托",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7b13f480-7488-43bc-91d3-41fcb5ab4c10",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 6395.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e3b671a3-54f6-4bc0-b9de-9f0138104164",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6395.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件委托是利用事件冒泡原理，管理某一类型的所有事件，利用父元素来代表子元素的某一类型事件的处理方式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1903e191-4b3c-4b42-9213-487417f3ced5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 6555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "已有元素的事件绑定",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c81cc123-7f82-49f7-bb2d-533a01e08c58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "事件委托机制的主要思想是将事件绑定至父元素上，然后利用事件冒泡原理，当事件进入冒泡阶段时，通过绑定在父元素上的事件对象来判断当前事件流正在进行的元素。如果和期望的元素相同，则执行相应的事件代码。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ebf4cd61-30c5-4155-9d6f-fb551ff41a8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 6795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "新创建元素的事件绑定",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe424eac-bc2e-4908-a38f-2f648a57b65d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6715.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8f51b727-4e13-4b89-816c-b85956378c3d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6715.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为我们通过querySelectorAll()函数获取到的元素虽然会实时感知到数量的变化，但并不会实时增加对事件的绑定。如果需要新元素也具有相同的事件，则需要手动调用事件绑定的代码。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f5727ade-6f81-47a7-ab1a-3a03dbb58065",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 6875.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "结局方案",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e4e5cdfe-7baa-45a0-b405-26073174b33d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 6875.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用事件委托机制，我们可以更加方便快捷地实现新创建元素的事件绑定。由于事件委托机制是利用的事件冒泡机制，即使在元素自身没有绑定事件的情况下，事件仍然会冒泡到父元素中，因此对于新增的元素，只要处理事件流就可以触发其事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7121f4a7-e455-4911-9afe-89e627ea7c52",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 7435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "文档加载完成事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "253090a3-6f16-48b9-9106-9c7578dff18b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 7115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8c230c4f-68e5-4574-a9a6-64430c583c38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在DOM中，文档加载完成有两个事件，一个是load事件，在原生JavaScript和jQuery中均有实现；另一个是jQuery提供的ready事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0ffdcd6d-29e8-41ec-b46d-43d95f0524b9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7035.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "ready事件的触发表示文档结构已经加载完成，不包含图片、flash等非文字媒体内容",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3711e71f-d1dc-47f5-9d0e-652f446b5863",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "onload事件的触发表示页面中包含的图片、flash等所有元素都加载完成",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "14320e10-2991-4253-b964-52f554dd3547",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 7435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "load事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6438723e-e669-4e3d-856b-926f3b7e18d6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "load事件会在页面、脚本或者图片加载完成后触发",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ceaef602-68cf-4ec5-a009-56bc938a34e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "支持onload事件的标签有body、frame、frameset、iframe、img、link、script",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2cbd9d76-e32a-4d41-8bbf-a7b59e8f1aba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 7755.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "body标签的onload事件和 window.onload的触发顺序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f298deaa-ba12-4828-a13b-d176cc59c015",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果window.onload在head标签中定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "aa573348-09aa-49d0-b386-ae5012929120",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "window.onload后执行，覆盖body标签的onload事件",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dcabb51b-567e-4460-be1f-1e0c81de3675",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 7835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果window.onload在body标签中定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4d118817-1948-464b-94ad-b45368e260a7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "body标签的onload事件后执行，覆盖window.onload",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "687b0e71-ee32-4388-a7be-2c543ed04597",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1730.3662298828126,
      "y": 10453.796298151765,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "浏览器的重排和重绘",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9b59e7bf-e67e-40e0-a1e5-9cc1622f8cc3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 8555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "浏览器渲染HTML的过程",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2a027879-dd6e-47e2-96f7-5205c1f27a58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 8235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "步骤",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ba014e25-8277-4bcc-b06c-eb2637be92f0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 7995.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "HTML文件被HTML解析器解析成对应的DOM树，CSS样式文件被CSS解析器解析生成对应的样式规则集",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "77ebe888-538d-43d5-9d5d-bd84741bc985",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8155.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DOM树与CSS样式集解析完成后，附加在一起形成一个渲染树",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3af5c93d-ca40-4ff0-9ab8-8a565deafce3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8315.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "节点信息的计算，即根据渲染树计算每个节点的几何信息",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "52a36b7f-87c0-47e6-b1a4-d4b2560136f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8475.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "渲染绘制，即根据计算完成的节点信息绘制整个页面",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1dd810ff-43cf-4f1b-b31e-08d12867ac82",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 8635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "示意图",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "defcedf2-2e0b-4769-a6c0-758693aabe8c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 8635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "defcedf2-2e0b-4769-a6c0-758693aabe8c",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9be101ec-185e-4e58-b870-1260ecd35b38",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 8795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重排和重绘发生在第3步和第4步中，正确地理解它们的关系将有助于我们使用一定的手段进行性能优化",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fc20a607-910e-47ff-8c02-58f7ffe4c439",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 9141.85185370732,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "背景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f659489f-7897-4273-8d58-0925c6f82a17",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 8955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "浏览器渲染页面默认采用的是流式布局模型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "da275e75-0d0e-4aea-a16a-30ecc0807ef0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 9115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为浏览器渲染页面是基于流式布局的，对某一个DOM节点信息进行修改时，就需要对该DOM结构进行重新计算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7982660a-dd34-4994-80ec-746fdaa47546",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 9355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "该DOM结构的修改会决定周边DOM结构的更改范围，主要分为全局范围和局部范围",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b3f4a6d0-9fd2-43c5-80d2-d02068db2eb1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9275.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "全局范围就是从页面的根节点html标签开始，对整个渲染树进行重新计算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "655c7c46-4bde-4574-84b4-6f9582327e28",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 9275.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "例如当我们改变窗口的尺寸或者修改了根元素的字体大小时",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "227fff92-0232-4953-a657-afb597bbc381",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "局部范围只会对渲染树的某部分进行重新计算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "463e3d35-72a3-4655-bfdc-58d8ba190038",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 9435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "例如要改变页面中某个div的宽度",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d455f36b-44b5-4e43-8a90-24091432dd93",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 9970.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重排",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "85c2c76e-ec5d-4d39-905f-5ec098d3348a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 9595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e692aea-7071-4dcc-93a5-06a1d4e9dc61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重排的过程就发生在DOM节点信息修改的时候，重排实际是根据渲染树中每个渲染对象的信息，计算出各自渲染对象的几何信息",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e0e7374b-e289-4642-a8b9-426a42dbc206",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 9595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "例如DOM元素的位置、尺寸、大小等，然后将其安置在界面中正确的位置",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d24ac85e-75e9-403c-86ff-be6eb2ce8f5d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 10345.185187040655,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见引起重排的操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8a004a5c-d239-4d7d-957b-c40532eb5846",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9755.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "页面首次渲染",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1483e3f9-8fd5-47f9-a241-dd9e5593eab4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 9755.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在页面首次渲染时，HTML页面的各个元素位置、尺寸、大小等信息均是未知的，需要通过与CSS样式规则集才能确定各个元素的几何信息。这个过程中会产生很多元素几何信息计算的过程，所以会产生重排操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "90175be6-3c6e-44fb-95e7-46bb59e784a9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 9915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "浏览器窗口大小发生改变",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "97728549-353a-48e1-a6bc-5f8d403a11c2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 9915.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "页面渲染完成后，就会得到一个固定的渲染树。如果此时对浏览器窗口进行缩放或者拉伸操作，渲染树中从根元素html标签开始的所有元素，都会重新计算其几何信息，从而产生重排操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e18acd7-27dd-4b95-8d2b-b5f82c009dd9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10075.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素尺寸或位置发生改变",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "81a4a055-2616-4e02-82fc-2a568a33cfd4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10235.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素内容发生变化",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d086d5c1-a68f-49bf-bb84-454e44b1fb8d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10395.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "元素内容发生变化",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "685c51cb-4f6d-49c8-8380-0d3d685e0626",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "添加或删除可见的DOM元素",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4ffc25de-a8a8-4341-bf76-91e5266149dc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 10555.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当前元素之后的元素会重新计算几何信息，渲染树也需要重新构建修改后的节点，从而产生重排操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d59881ce-013c-4b5e-8c24-4656e0b9d250",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 10795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获取某些特定的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8f2ace30-fab5-4789-9928-4b9efde40f13",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 10715.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "频繁的重排操作会对浏览器引擎产生很大的消耗。所以浏览器不会针对每个JS操作都进行一次重排，而是维护一个会引起重排操作的队列，等队列中的操作达到了一定的数量或者到了一定的时间间隔时，浏览器才会去flush一次队列，进行真正的重排操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e3fa86b6-e762-4638-a76f-633cab32b49d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 10875.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "但是浏览器为了返回最精准的信息，需要flush队列，因为队列中的某些操作可能会影响到某些值的获取。因此，即使你获取的样式信息与队列中的操作无关，浏览器仍然会强制flush队列，从而引起浏览器重排的操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0e1251c-c267-4c5a-a2fe-3a93a289bbb8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11035.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "会导致渲染树中相关的节点失效，浏览器会根据DOM元素的变化，重新构建渲染树中失效的节点，从而产生重排操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6d63d49c-c009-445a-bf29-7fbd083545d0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 11195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重绘",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5e42ae39-c581-4147-8683-c9eb924d6297",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 11195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a71bd0f1-eab7-4bc0-bf4e-f7f5ea8b225e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重绘只是改变元素在页面中的展现样式，而不会引起元素在文档流中位置的改变",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "41c17587-134e-4447-9ae0-0329766b14b6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 11195.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "例如更改了元素的字体颜色、背景色、透明度等，浏览器均会将这些新样式赋予元素并重新绘制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b73084cc-39c6-4507-9356-2bf011d4307f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 11355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重排和重绘的关系",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "287e6e73-1e6c-47b2-8281-ba7471e22e42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 11355.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重排一定会引起重绘的操作，而重绘却不一定会引起重排的操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "97f4a49a-8ec3-498c-bcd4-4c46b88f985e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2150.3662298828126,
      "y": 12505.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "性能优化",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d54cb8de-ac10-423b-8d49-a64969a8fd5b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 11595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将多次改变样式的属性操作合并为一次",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4f1c3744-ee9f-4b2a-8242-4b1bd188da77",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改前",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "023a09e7-c91a-4020-88d8-34340b1bdc2f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 11515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var changeDiv = document.querySelector('#changeDiv');\nchangeDiv.style.width = '100px';\n\nchangeDiv.style.background = '#e3e3e3';\n\nchangeDiv.style.height = '100px';\n\nchangeDiv.style.marginTop = '10px';",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "352d9745-6eee-4e3c-924f-5539dd36f1db",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改后",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe4944aa-66b1-4054-9c64-38d239a4b8a7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 11675.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "div.changeDiv {\n    width: '100px',\n\n    background: #e3e3e3;\n\n    height: 100px;\n\n    margin-top: 10px;\n\n}\n\ndocument.getElementById('changeDiv').className = 'changeDiv';",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "434def8f-0514-40e2-993d-83acfe6c62ac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 11835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将需要多次重排的元素设置为绝对定位",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3eee9cad-a899-4078-b160-29d306bfcbe2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "需要进行重排的元素都是处于正常的文档流中的，如果这个元素不处于文档流中，那么它的变化就不会影响到其他元素的变化，这样就不会引起重排的操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6f95c33e-e47e-432d-bd22-c25248a35679",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 11835.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见的操作就是设置其position为absolute或者fixed",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b555c687-a158-4259-a594-9ef56bcddc77",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 12075.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在内存中多次操作节点，完成后再添加至文档树中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bbf0ffa8-6070-42e7-9d39-2dedaeb71479",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 11995.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改前",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "69efbb2c-fa98-4e86-9797-6b495e91c4f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 11995.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "每次构造一行数据的HTML片段，分多次添加到文档树中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6ab405f2-83ea-44ef-82c9-c677ee24f17d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12155.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "修改后",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2a46ed43-8966-4ba8-821b-3f60edddd30b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3410.3662298828126,
      "y": 12155.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "先在内存中构建出完整的HTML片段，再一次性添加到文档树中",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f9bb7704-f0bc-430c-8a68-d04576fc7e4f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 12395.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将要进行复杂处理的元素处理为display属性为none，处理完成后再进行显示",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7df83ccb-9843-4302-8a81-4dedb41ab30e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12315.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为display属性为none的元素不会出现在渲染树中，所以对其进行处理并不会引起其他元素的重排。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c94cc01c-6450-4f61-92f6-0f1eee530805",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12475.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当我们需要对一个元素做复杂处理时，可以将其display属性设置为none，操作完成后，再将其显示出来，这样就只会在隐藏和显示的时候引发两次重排操作",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1b87147c-4ca0-4e69-93e0-9ec5e583229e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 12635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将频繁获取会引起重排的属性缓存至变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "05d76355-02fa-4043-8735-d701836c61f9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12635.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在获取一些特定属性时，会引发重排或者重绘的操作。因此在获取这些属性时，我们应该通过一个变量去缓存，而不是每次都直接获取特定的属性",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0ba5bffd-281e-4394-80bf-27aa90de3820",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 12875.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "尽量减少使用table布局",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "87740785-8be4-4ddd-b2bd-c889e83a7a23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12795.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果table中任何一个元素触发了重排的操作，那么整个table都会触发重排的操作，尤其是当一个table内容比较庞大时，更加不推荐使用table布局",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "37bf1cfc-a968-4aa4-af6a-902e26db1f54",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 12955.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果不得已使用了table，可以设置table-layout:auto或者是table-layout:fixed。这样可以让table一行一行地渲染，这种做法也是为了限制重排的影响范围",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b80b26bd-e471-412b-9b17-90bd23f6a2b7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 13115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用事件委托绑定事件处理程序",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0bd4d34d-6ffa-4d4a-8d4a-592b25aabd6f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13115.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在对多个同级元素做事件绑定时，推荐使用事件委托机制进行处理。使用事件委托可以在很大程度上减少事件处理程序的数量，从而提高性能",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e4d2d786-7593-45b6-b87c-ef8607df3094",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2570.3662298828126,
      "y": 13515.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "利用DocumentFragment操作DOM节点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d667b900-b360-4852-9686-96dc617f18e4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13275.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DocumentFragment是一个没有父级节点的最小文档对象，它可以用于存储已经排好版或者尚未确定格式的HTML片段。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1cede257-188d-4a3d-adac-f70b9c46b48a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13435.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "DocumentFragment最核心的知识点在于它不是真实DOM树的一部分，它的变化不会引起DOM树重新渲染的操作，也就不会引起浏览器重排和重绘的操作，从而带来性能上的提升",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e10dadcd-e3cd-43d2-9aad-240dbeea52ca",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13595.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为DocumentFragment具有的特性，在需要频繁进行DOM新增或者删除的操作中，它将变得非常有用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5cb7e4d-0e6b-49cc-9e12-a767017f3b39",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2990.3662298828126,
      "y": 13755.185187040654,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用DocumentFragment()函数处理DOM元素时，只有在最终append的时候才会去真正处理真实的DOM元素，因此只会引发一次重排操作，从而提升了浏览器渲染的性能",
      "color": "5"
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
